## How to merge or discard

To merge:

```bash
cd <project root, NOT the worktree>
git merge autorun/<TS> --no-ff
```

To discard:

```bash
cd <project root>
git worktree remove ../<repo>_autorun_<TS> --force
git branch -D autorun/<TS>
```
